<v-list expand light>
  <v-list-group
    v-for="item in items"
    v-model="item.active"
    :key="item.title"
    :prepend-icon="item.action"
  >
    <v-list-tile slot="activator">
      <v-list-tile-content>
        <v-list-tile-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-tile-title>
      </v-list-tile-content>
    </v-list-tile>

    <v-list-tile
      v-for="subItem in item.items"
      :key="subItem.title"
      :to="subItem.link"
      @click="select_category(subItem.category)"
    >
      <v-list-tile-content>
        <v-list-tile-title>{{ subItem.title }}</v-list-tile-title>
      </v-list-tile-content>
      <v-list-tile-action>
        <v-icon>{{ subItem.action }}</v-icon>
      </v-list-tile-action>
    </v-list-tile>
  </v-list-group>
</v-list>
